<h2>Help</h2>
<p>
This is a game where you can train your calories guessing skills by training with a database of popular groceries items.
</p>
<p>Sign up and log in to keep track of scores and stats.</p>
<p>For each game, there are 5 guesses. The hot-warm-cold hints can guide you closer to the correct answer. 
If your guess is within a small range of the correct answer, you can score points. The closer the guess is, the higher the score.</p>

